---
title: Caramelized Veggie Skewers with Summer Corn Relish and Herby Couscous
description: Skewers are made for summer—they’re easy, transportable, and perfect for the grill! These veggie skewers are loaded up with mushrooms, zucchini, and bell peppers, then popped under the broiler for major caramelization. A side of tangy corn relish is the perfect accompaniment!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caramelized-veggie-skewers-b2c3424c.jpg
